  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, heat the sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion, carrot, and celery, and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, white vinegar, salt, and black pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and add the silken tofu, breaking it up with a spoon.",
    "Simmer the mixture for 10 minutes, or until the soup has thickened slightly.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the Xtra Velvety Korean Tofu Guk hot, garnished with chopped green onions if desired.",
    "Let the soup cool before refrigerating or freezing for later use."
